705744f-a.text:
Moffat Street, north of Knickerbocker Ave., showing in the background the mansion of J.E. Van Nostrand, which was demolished in April 1929. This ie a set of 2 views showing same in Queens County at Wyckoff and
Cooper Aves.
November 1923.
View 2:-January 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
